Installer Dapr CLI :
iwr -useb https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dapr/cli/master/install/install.ps1 | iex
dapr init
ajouter    C:\dapr     à PATH (env variables)

dapr dashboard -k

Installer kubectl: 
curl.exe -LO "https://dl.k8s.io/release/v1.32.0/bin/windows/amd64/kubectl.exe"

Copiez kubectl.exe dans C:\Windows\System32
ajouter    C:\Windows\System32\kubectl.exe    à PATH (env variables)


Installer Minikube:
https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/?arch=%2Fwindows%2Fx86-64%2Fstable%2F.exe+download

minikube start --driver=hyperv --memory=1900 --disk-size=10g

